instructions: Put the charger on the bottom edge of the table
Put the dinner fork to the left of the charger with the tines facing up
put the dinner knife to the right of the charger, vertically with the blade facing to the left
put the salad for to the left of the dinner fork, with the tines facing up
put the salad knife to the right of the dinner knife, vertically with the blade facing to the left
put the soup spoon to the right of the salad knife with the bowl facing up
center the dessert spoon above the charger with the bowl facing left
place the dessert fork between the dessert spoon and the charger, with the tines facing right
place the bread plate above the dinner and salad forks, place the dinner plate in the center of the charger
place the butter knife diagonally on the bread plate with the point in the upper left
place the water glass above the knives and soup spoon
place the napkin horizontally in the middle of the dinner plate
